{"tid":2123151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國《財富》雜誌預言九七之後香港大倒退","createTime":"2020-07-24T12:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T03:09:30.000Z","uid":51546,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"930a082370133a34bd8a864918e482ba8ac3a8ef","tid":2123151,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"1995年美國《財富》雜誌封面以「香港之死」為題，預言九七之後香港大倒退。<br />\n<br />\n文章中所謂「香港之死」，並非經濟上完蛋，香港仍是富豪的樂園，仍然是一個「能賺很多錢的地方」。但文章預言隨著香港「變成北京的殖民地」、「變成一個普通的中國城市」，「以裙帶關係與貪腐方式管治」而「不再重視法治」，香港將變成「一潭死水」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，文章預言「英語將會凋零」、「倚賴廣東話與普通話」；北京「將控制全部政府部門」、「立法會議員換上服從的人」、「選擇肯合作的法官」、「委任行政長官」、「大阿哥馴服傳媒，逼令自我審查」。<br />\n<br />\n今日重看，已有不少應驗。<br />\n<br />\n(摘自重讀〈香港之死〉)"},{"pid":"627a03df55a08b47e222e0e4a04519fdfde5c369","tid":2123151,"uid":51546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"當年好多人笑呢本雜誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcf446136885752c6bdd7e374c15761cdcfc3ca","tid":2123151,"uid":41116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"d支媒最鐘意cap段 title黎打J<br />\n話香港仲好好 未死<br />\n<br />\n香港係唔會死 但係我知嘅香港已經死左"},{"pid":"d10d96b70e75190adf2daa7c1885e07d7c4f51e1","tid":2123151,"uid":56957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"627a03df55a08b47e222e0e4a04519fdfde5c369","tid":2123151,"uid":51546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"當年好多人笑呢本雜誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"當年嗰班咪係發生完六四都對剩係識賺錢抄賣對回歸無感覺嗰班"},{"pid":"b2e805b59f71a1c7a2c33b97d3cabc2041797106","tid":2123151,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"